# owner: project maintainer
# date: 2026-03-23
# purpose: production-oriented environment example for the Searcharr-nxg compose runtime
# docs: README.md, maintainer/README.md
# deployment notes:
#   - Provide a real settings.py outside Git and point PROJECT_SETTINGS_FILE at it.
#   - Pin PROJECT_IMAGE to a built or published Searcharr-nxg image tag.
# history:
#   - 2026-03-10: Initialized generic template example.
#   - 2026-03-23: Adapted the example for Searcharr-nxg.

# Container image pinned for deployment.
PROJECT_IMAGE=ghcr.io/brainponders/searcharr-nxg:v1.0.0

# Container identity and settings bind mount.
PROJECT_CONTAINER_NAME=searcharr-nxg
PROJECT_SETTINGS_FILE=./config/settings.py
